@startuml SequenceAIChat

actor 用户
participant "AIChatBoundary" as AIB
participant "AIChatControl" as AIC
participant "AIConversation (Entity)" as ACE
participant "AIService (External)" as AIS
database "Database" as DB

用户 -> AIB: 发送消息 "我最近睡眠不好"
AIB -> AIC: send_chat_message(message)

AIC -> ACE: 保存用户消息
ACE -> DB: INSERT INTO ai_conversations

AIC -> DB: 查询最近7天健康记录
DB --> AIC: HealthRecord 列表

AIC -> DB: 查询最近8条对话历史
DB --> AIC: Conversation 列表

AIC -> AIC: build_health_context(user, records)
AIC -> AIC: build_messages(system_prompt, history, message)

AIC -> AIS: POST /chat/completions

alt API 调用成功
  AIS --> AIC: AI 生成的回复
else API 不可用
  AIS --> AIC: 网络错误
  AIC -> AIC: _fallback_response(规则引擎)
end

AIC -> ACE: 保存助手回复
ACE -> DB: INSERT INTO ai_conversations

AIC --> AIB: 返回回复内容
AIB --> 用户: 显示 AI 回复

@enduml
